channel.title: Funeral
channel.description:
Me and Ruppich were talking on MSN and we decided to host a funeral on Runescape. To attend you must post your runescape name on this thread. We will meet in the Lumbridge church, World 74(non-members) my runescape name will be Last Stand42, the funeral will happen 11:00 P.M. Eastern Daylight Time, Michigan, United States. If you have nothing nice to say, don't say anything at all. Me and a volenteer wil be the preacher. Someone who knew him well or was a friend to him.
Warning: I do know know sL that much, i usually talked to him on IRC. Please do not flame me.
Thank You
